---
/**
 * Homepage-only "exposure" entry animation.
 *
 * Film-development feel: the logo emerges from darkness like a frame being
 * exposed — blur and brightness resolve gradually while a faint amber
 * vignette breathes once. No moving parts; pure light and focus.
 *
 * Safe by default: CSS-hidden unless the head bootstrap marks the document as
 * entry-pending. If JS fails, content stays fully readable.
 */
---

